Commands With Successful Output
1. Start Hive Local Mode
beeline -u "jdbc:hive2:///;transportMode=local"
✅ Successful connection.

2. Show Databases
SHOW DATABASES;
✅ Output appeared.

3. Create Database
CREATE DATABASE flightdb;
✅ Database created.

4. Use Database
USE flightdb;
✅ Database selected.

5. Create Flights Table
CREATE TABLE flights (
    flight_id INT,
    airline STRING,
    source STRING,
    destination STRING,
    departure_delay INT,
    flight_date STRING
)
ROW FORMAT DELIMITED
FIELDS TERMINATED BY ',';
✅ Table created.

6. Show Tables
SHOW TABLES;
✅ Output showed tables.

7. Load CSV Data
LOAD DATA LOCAL INPATH '/Users/arpit/flights.csv'
INTO TABLE flights;
✅ Data loaded.

8. Select Data
SELECT * FROM flights;
✅ Records displayed successfully.

9. Insert New Record
SET hive.execution.engine=mr;
SET mapreduce.framework.name=local;
INSERT INTO flights VALUES
(5,'Akasa','Mumbai','Goa',25,'2008-01-03');
✅ Insert successful.

10. Alter Table
ALTER TABLE flights
ADD COLUMNS (status STRING);
✅ Column added.

11. Describe Table
DESCRIBE flights;
✅ Table structure displayed.

12. Create External Table
CREATE EXTERNAL TABLE ext_flights (
    flight_id INT,
    airline STRING,
    source STRING,
    destination STRING,
    departure_delay INT,
    flight_date STRING
)
ROW FORMAT DELIMITED
FIELDS TERMINATED BY ','
LOCATION '/tmp/ext_flights';
✅ External table created.

13. Create Airlines Table
CREATE TABLE airlines (
    airline STRING,
    country STRING
)
ROW FORMAT DELIMITED
FIELDS TERMINATED BY ',';
✅ Table created.

14. Insert Into Airlines
INSERT INTO airlines VALUES
('Indigo','India'),
('AirIndia','India'),
('SpiceJet','India'),
('Vistara','India'),
('Akasa','India');
✅ Insert successful.

15. Average Departure Delay Query
SELECT flight_date,
AVG(departure_delay) AS avg_delay
FROM flights
WHERE flight_date LIKE '2008%'
GROUP BY flight_date;
✅ Analytical query works and gives output.

