Index Commands
These may fail on Hive 4 because indexes are deprecated:
CREATE INDEX flight_index
ON TABLE flights (airline)
AS 'COMPACT'
WITH DEFERRED REBUILD;
So if index failed, it is normal in newer Hive versions.


